{"response":{"verses":[{"auditid":"0","verse":"1","lastverse":"1","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.25.1","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Sam.25.1","label":"","reference":"1 Samuel 25:1","prev_osis_id":"1Sam.024.023,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Sam.025.002,fra-LSG","text":"<h3 class=\"s\">Mort de Samuel. \u2014 Duret\u00e9 de Nabal envers David, et prudence de sa femme Abiga\u00efl<\/h3>\n<h5 class=\"r\">V. 1-35: cf. (\u00c9s 32:5-8. Ps 73:1-9.) (Pr 20:22; 15:1, 23, 31; 25:11.)<\/h5>\n<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Sam.25.1\" class=\"v\">1<\/sup>\n    Samuel mourut. Tout Isra\u00ebl s\u2019\u00e9tant assembl\u00e9 le pleura, et on l\u2019enterra dans sa demeure \u00e0 Rama. Ce fut alors que David se leva et descendit au d\u00e9sert de Paran.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Sam.25","name":"1 Samuel 25","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.25"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Sam.25.2","name":"1 Samuel 25:2","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.25.2"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Sam.24.23","name":"1 Samuel 24:23","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.24.23"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"2","lastverse":"2","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.25.2","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Sam.25.2","label":"","reference":"1 Samuel 25:2","prev_osis_id":"1Sam.025.001,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Sam.025.003,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Sam.25.2\" class=\"v\">2<\/sup>Il y avait \u00e0 Maon un homme fort riche, poss\u00e9dant des biens \u00e0 Carmel; il avait trois mille brebis et mille ch\u00e8vres, et il se trouvait \u00e0 Carmel pour la tonte de ses brebis.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Sam.25","name":"1 Samuel 25","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.25"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Sam.25.3","name":"1 Samuel 25:3","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.25.3"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Sam.25.1","name":"1 Samuel 25:1","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.25.1"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"3","lastverse":"3","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.25.3","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Sam.25.3","label":"","reference":"1 Samuel 25:3","prev_osis_id":"1Sam.025.002,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Sam.025.004,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Sam.25.3\" class=\"v\">3<\/sup>Le nom de cet homme \u00e9tait Nabal, et sa femme s\u2019appelait Abiga\u00efl; c\u2019\u00e9tait une femme de bon sens et belle de figure, mais l\u2019homme \u00e9tait dur et m\u00e9chant dans ses actions. Il descendait de Caleb.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Sam.25","name":"1 Samuel 25","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.25"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Sam.25.4","name":"1 Samuel 25:4","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.25.4"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Sam.25.2","name":"1 Samuel 25:2","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.25.2"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"4","lastverse":"4","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.25.4","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Sam.25.4","label":"","reference":"1 Samuel 25:4","prev_osis_id":"1Sam.025.003,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Sam.025.005,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Sam.25.4\" class=\"v\">4<\/sup>David apprit au d\u00e9sert que Nabal tondait ses brebis.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Sam.25","name":"1 Samuel 25","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.25"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Sam.25.5","name":"1 Samuel 25:5","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.25.5"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Sam.25.3","name":"1 Samuel 25:3","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.25.3"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"5","lastverse":"5","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.25.5","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Sam.25.5","label":"","reference":"1 Samuel 25:5","prev_osis_id":"1Sam.025.004,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Sam.025.006,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Sam.25.5\" class=\"v\">5<\/sup>Il envoya vers lui dix jeunes gens, auxquels il dit: Montez \u00e0 Carmel, et allez aupr\u00e8s de Nabal. Vous le saluerez en mon nom,<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Sam.25","name":"1 Samuel 25","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.25"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Sam.25.6","name":"1 Samuel 25:6","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.25.6"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Sam.25.4","name":"1 Samuel 25:4","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.25.4"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"6","lastverse":"6","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.25.6","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Sam.25.6","label":"","reference":"1 Samuel 25:6","prev_osis_id":"1Sam.025.005,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Sam.025.007,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Sam.25.6\" class=\"v\">6<\/sup>et vous lui parlerez ainsi: Pour la vie sois en paix, et que la paix soit avec ta maison et tout ce qui t\u2019appartient!<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Sam.25","name":"1 Samuel 25","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.25"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Sam.25.7","name":"1 Samuel 25:7","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.25.7"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Sam.25.5","name":"1 Samuel 25:5","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.25.5"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"7","lastverse":"7","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.25.7","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Sam.25.7","label":"","reference":"1 Samuel 25:7","prev_osis_id":"1Sam.025.006,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Sam.025.008,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Sam.25.7\" class=\"v\">7<\/sup>Et maintenant, j\u2019ai appris que tu as les tondeurs. Or tes bergers ont \u00e9t\u00e9 avec nous; nous ne leur avons fait aucun outrage, et rien ne leur a \u00e9t\u00e9 enlev\u00e9 pendant tout le temps qu\u2019ils ont \u00e9t\u00e9 \u00e0 Carmel.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Sam.25","name":"1 Samuel 25","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.25"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Sam.25.8","name":"1 Samuel 25:8","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.25.8"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Sam.25.6","name":"1 Samuel 25:6","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.25.6"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"8","lastverse":"8","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.25.8","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Sam.25.8","label":"","reference":"1 Samuel 25:8","prev_osis_id":"1Sam.025.007,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Sam.025.009,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Sam.25.8\" class=\"v\">8<\/sup>Demande-le \u00e0 tes serviteurs, et ils te le diront. Que ces jeunes gens trouvent donc gr\u00e2ce \u00e0 tes yeux, puisque nous venons dans un jour de joie. Donne donc, je te prie, \u00e0 tes serviteurs et \u00e0 ton fils David ce qui se trouvera sous ta main.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Sam.25","name":"1 Samuel 25","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.25"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Sam.25.9","name":"1 Samuel 25:9","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.25.9"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Sam.25.7","name":"1 Samuel 25:7","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.25.7"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"9","lastverse":"9","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.25.9","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Sam.25.9","label":"","reference":"1 Samuel 25:9","prev_osis_id":"1Sam.025.008,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Sam.025.010,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Sam.25.9\" class=\"v\">9<\/sup>Lorsque les gens de David furent arriv\u00e9s, ils r\u00e9p\u00e9t\u00e8rent \u00e0 Nabal toutes ces paroles, au nom de David. Puis ils se turent.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Sam.25","name":"1 Samuel 25","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.25"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Sam.25.10","name":"1 Samuel 25:10","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.25.10"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Sam.25.8","name":"1 Samuel 25:8","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.25.8"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"10","lastverse":"10","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.25.10","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Sam.25.10","label":"","reference":"1 Samuel 25:10","prev_osis_id":"1Sam.025.009,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Sam.025.011,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Sam.25.10\" class=\"v\">10<\/sup>Nabal r\u00e9pondit aux serviteurs de David: Qui est David, et qui est le fils d\u2019Isa\u00ef? Il y a aujourd\u2019hui beaucoup de serviteurs qui s\u2019\u00e9chappent d\u2019aupr\u00e8s de leurs ma\u00eetres.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Sam.25","name":"1 Samuel 25","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.25"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Sam.25.11","name":"1 Samuel 25:11","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.25.11"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Sam.25.9","name":"1 Samuel 25:9","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.25.9"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"11","lastverse":"11","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.25.11","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Sam.25.11","label":"","reference":"1 Samuel 25:11","prev_osis_id":"1Sam.025.010,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Sam.025.012,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Sam.25.11\" class=\"v\">11<\/sup>Et je prendrais mon pain, mon eau, et mon b\u00e9tail que j\u2019ai tu\u00e9 pour mes tondeurs, et je les donnerais \u00e0 des gens qui sont je ne sais d\u2019o\u00f9?<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Sam.25","name":"1 Samuel 25","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.25"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Sam.25.12","name":"1 Samuel 25:12","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.25.12"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Sam.25.10","name":"1 Samuel 25:10","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.25.10"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"12","lastverse":"12","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.25.12","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Sam.25.12","label":"","reference":"1 Samuel 25:12","prev_osis_id":"1Sam.025.011,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Sam.025.013,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Sam.25.12\" class=\"v\">12<\/sup>Les gens de David rebrouss\u00e8rent chemin; ils s\u2019en retourn\u00e8rent, et redirent, \u00e0 leur arriv\u00e9e, toutes ces paroles \u00e0 David.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Sam.25","name":"1 Samuel 25","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.25"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Sam.25.13","name":"1 Samuel 25:13","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.25.13"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Sam.25.11","name":"1 Samuel 25:11","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.25.11"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"13","lastverse":"13","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.25.13","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Sam.25.13","label":"","reference":"1 Samuel 25:13","prev_osis_id":"1Sam.025.012,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Sam.025.014,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Sam.25.13\" class=\"v\">13<\/sup>Alors David dit \u00e0 ses gens: Que chacun de vous ceigne son \u00e9p\u00e9e! Et ils ceignirent chacun leur \u00e9p\u00e9e. David aussi ceignit son \u00e9p\u00e9e, et environ quatre cents hommes mont\u00e8rent \u00e0 sa suite. Il en resta deux cents pr\u00e8s des bagages.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Sam.25","name":"1 Samuel 25","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.25"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Sam.25.14","name":"1 Samuel 25:14","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.25.14"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Sam.25.12","name":"1 Samuel 25:12","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.25.12"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"14","lastverse":"14","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.25.14","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Sam.25.14","label":"","reference":"1 Samuel 25:14","prev_osis_id":"1Sam.025.013,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Sam.025.015,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Sam.25.14\" class=\"v\">14<\/sup>Un des serviteurs de Nabal vint dire \u00e0 Abiga\u00efl, femme de Nabal: Voici, David a envoy\u00e9 du d\u00e9sert des messagers pour saluer notre ma\u00eetre, qui les a rudoy\u00e9s.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Sam.25","name":"1 Samuel 25","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.25"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Sam.25.15","name":"1 Samuel 25:15","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.25.15"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Sam.25.13","name":"1 Samuel 25:13","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.25.13"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"15","lastverse":"15","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.25.15","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Sam.25.15","label":"","reference":"1 Samuel 25:15","prev_osis_id":"1Sam.025.014,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Sam.025.016,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Sam.25.15\" class=\"v\">15<\/sup>Et pourtant ces gens ont \u00e9t\u00e9 tr\u00e8s bons pour nous; ils ne nous ont fait aucun outrage, et rien ne nous a \u00e9t\u00e9 enlev\u00e9, tout le temps que nous avons \u00e9t\u00e9 avec eux lorsque nous \u00e9tions dans les champs.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Sam.25","name":"1 Samuel 25","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.25"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Sam.25.16","name":"1 Samuel 25:16","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.25.16"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Sam.25.14","name":"1 Samuel 25:14","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.25.14"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"16","lastverse":"16","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.25.16","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Sam.25.16","label":"","reference":"1 Samuel 25:16","prev_osis_id":"1Sam.025.015,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Sam.025.017,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Sam.25.16\" class=\"v\">16<\/sup>Ils nous ont nuit et jour servi de muraille, tout le temps que nous avons \u00e9t\u00e9 avec eux, faisant pa\u00eetre les troupeaux.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Sam.25","name":"1 Samuel 25","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.25"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Sam.25.17","name":"1 Samuel 25:17","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.25.17"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Sam.25.15","name":"1 Samuel 25:15","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.25.15"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"17","lastverse":"17","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.25.17","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Sam.25.17","label":"","reference":"1 Samuel 25:17","prev_osis_id":"1Sam.025.016,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Sam.025.018,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Sam.25.17\" class=\"v\">17<\/sup>Sache maintenant et vois ce que tu as \u00e0 faire, car la perte de notre ma\u00eetre et de toute sa maison est r\u00e9solue, et il est si m\u00e9chant qu\u2019on n\u2019ose lui parler.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Sam.25","name":"1 Samuel 25","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.25"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Sam.25.18","name":"1 Samuel 25:18","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.25.18"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Sam.25.16","name":"1 Samuel 25:16","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.25.16"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"18","lastverse":"18","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.25.18","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Sam.25.18","label":"","reference":"1 Samuel 25:18","prev_osis_id":"1Sam.025.017,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Sam.025.019,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Sam.25.18\" class=\"v\">18<\/sup>Abiga\u00efl prit aussit\u00f4t deux cents pains, deux outres de vin, cinq pi\u00e8ces de b\u00e9tail appr\u00eat\u00e9es, cinq mesures de grain r\u00f4ti, cent masses de raisins secs, et deux cents de figues s\u00e8ches. Elle les mit sur des \u00e2nes,<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Sam.25","name":"1 Samuel 25","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.25"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Sam.25.19","name":"1 Samuel 25:19","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.25.19"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Sam.25.17","name":"1 Samuel 25:17","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.25.17"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"19","lastverse":"19","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.25.19","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Sam.25.19","label":"","reference":"1 Samuel 25:19","prev_osis_id":"1Sam.025.018,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Sam.025.020,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Sam.25.19\" class=\"v\">19<\/sup>et elle dit \u00e0 ses serviteurs: Passez devant moi, je vais vous suivre. Elle ne dit rien \u00e0 Nabal, son mari.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Sam.25","name":"1 Samuel 25","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.25"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Sam.25.20","name":"1 Samuel 25:20","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.25.20"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Sam.25.18","name":"1 Samuel 25:18","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.25.18"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"20","lastverse":"20","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.25.20","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Sam.25.20","label":"","reference":"1 Samuel 25:20","prev_osis_id":"1Sam.025.019,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Sam.025.021,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Sam.25.20\" class=\"v\">20<\/sup>Mont\u00e9e sur un \u00e2ne, elle descendit la montagne par un chemin couvert; et voici, David et ses gens descendaient en face d\u2019elle, en sorte qu\u2019elle les rencontra.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Sam.25","name":"1 Samuel 25","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.25"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Sam.25.21","name":"1 Samuel 25:21","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.25.21"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Sam.25.19","name":"1 Samuel 25:19","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.25.19"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"21","lastverse":"21","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.25.21","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Sam.25.21","label":"","reference":"1 Samuel 25:21","prev_osis_id":"1Sam.025.020,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Sam.025.022,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Sam.25.21\" class=\"v\">21<\/sup>David avait dit: C\u2019est bien en vain que j\u2019ai gard\u00e9 tout ce que cet homme a dans le d\u00e9sert, et que rien n\u2019a \u00e9t\u00e9 enlev\u00e9 de tout ce qu\u2019il poss\u00e8de; il m\u2019a rendu le mal pour le bien.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Sam.25","name":"1 Samuel 25","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.25"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Sam.25.22","name":"1 Samuel 25:22","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.25.22"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Sam.25.20","name":"1 Samuel 25:20","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.25.20"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"22","lastverse":"22","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.25.22","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Sam.25.22","label":"","reference":"1 Samuel 25:22","prev_osis_id":"1Sam.025.021,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Sam.025.023,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Sam.25.22\" class=\"v\">22<\/sup>Que Dieu traite son serviteur David dans toute sa rigueur, si je laisse subsister jusqu\u2019\u00e0 la lumi\u00e8re du matin qui que ce soit de tout ce qui appartient \u00e0 Nabal!<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Sam.25","name":"1 Samuel 25","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.25"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Sam.25.23","name":"1 Samuel 25:23","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.25.23"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Sam.25.21","name":"1 Samuel 25:21","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.25.21"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"23","lastverse":"23","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.25.23","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Sam.25.23","label":"","reference":"1 Samuel 25:23","prev_osis_id":"1Sam.025.022,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Sam.025.024,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Sam.25.23\" class=\"v\">23<\/sup>Lorsque Abiga\u00efl aper\u00e7ut David, elle descendit rapidement de l\u2019\u00e2ne, tomba sur sa face en pr\u00e9sence de David, et se prosterna contre terre.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Sam.25","name":"1 Samuel 25","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.25"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Sam.25.24","name":"1 Samuel 25:24","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.25.24"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Sam.25.22","name":"1 Samuel 25:22","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.25.22"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"24","lastverse":"24","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.25.24","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Sam.25.24","label":"","reference":"1 Samuel 25:24","prev_osis_id":"1Sam.025.023,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Sam.025.025,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Sam.25.24\" class=\"v\">24<\/sup>Puis, se jetant \u00e0 ses pieds, elle dit: A moi la faute, mon seigneur! Permets \u00e0 ta servante de parler \u00e0 tes oreilles, et \u00e9coute les paroles de ta servante.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Sam.25","name":"1 Samuel 25","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.25"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Sam.25.25","name":"1 Samuel 25:25","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.25.25"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Sam.25.23","name":"1 Samuel 25:23","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.25.23"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"25","lastverse":"25","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.25.25","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Sam.25.25","label":"","reference":"1 Samuel 25:25","prev_osis_id":"1Sam.025.024,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Sam.025.026,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Sam.25.25\" class=\"v\">25<\/sup>Que mon seigneur ne prenne pas garde \u00e0 ce m\u00e9chant homme, \u00e0 Nabal, car il est comme son nom; Nabal est son nom, et il y a chez lui de la folie. Et moi, ta servante, je n\u2019ai pas vu les gens que mon seigneur a envoy\u00e9s.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Sam.25","name":"1 Samuel 25","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.25"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Sam.25.26","name":"1 Samuel 25:26","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.25.26"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Sam.25.24","name":"1 Samuel 25:24","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.25.24"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"26","lastverse":"26","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.25.26","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Sam.25.26","label":"","reference":"1 Samuel 25:26","prev_osis_id":"1Sam.025.025,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Sam.025.027,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Sam.25.26\" class=\"v\">26<\/sup>Maintenant, mon seigneur, aussi vrai que l\u2019\u00c9ternel est vivant et que ton \u00e2me est vivante, c\u2019est l\u2019\u00c9ternel qui t\u2019a emp\u00each\u00e9 de r\u00e9pandre le sang et qui a retenu ta main. Que tes ennemis, que ceux qui veulent du mal \u00e0 mon seigneur soient comme Nabal!<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Sam.25","name":"1 Samuel 25","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.25"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Sam.25.27","name":"1 Samuel 25:27","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.25.27"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Sam.25.25","name":"1 Samuel 25:25","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.25.25"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"27","lastverse":"27","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.25.27","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Sam.25.27","label":"","reference":"1 Samuel 25:27","prev_osis_id":"1Sam.025.026,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Sam.025.028,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Sam.25.27\" class=\"v\">27<\/sup>Accepte ce pr\u00e9sent que ta servante apporte \u00e0 mon seigneur, et qu\u2019il soit distribu\u00e9 aux gens qui marchent \u00e0 la suite de mon seigneur.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Sam.25","name":"1 Samuel 25","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.25"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Sam.25.28","name":"1 Samuel 25:28","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.25.28"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Sam.25.26","name":"1 Samuel 25:26","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.25.26"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"28","lastverse":"28","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.25.28","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Sam.25.28","label":"","reference":"1 Samuel 25:28","prev_osis_id":"1Sam.025.027,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Sam.025.029,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Sam.25.28\" class=\"v\">28<\/sup>Pardonne, je te prie, la faute de ta servante, car l\u2019\u00c9ternel fera \u00e0 mon seigneur une maison stable; pardonne, car mon seigneur soutient les guerres de l\u2019\u00c9ternel, et la m\u00e9chancet\u00e9 ne se trouvera jamais en toi.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Sam.25","name":"1 Samuel 25","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.25"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Sam.25.29","name":"1 Samuel 25:29","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.25.29"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Sam.25.27","name":"1 Samuel 25:27","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.25.27"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"29","lastverse":"29","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.25.29","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Sam.25.29","label":"","reference":"1 Samuel 25:29","prev_osis_id":"1Sam.025.028,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Sam.025.030,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Sam.25.29\" class=\"v\">29<\/sup>S\u2019il s\u2019\u00e9l\u00e8ve quelqu\u2019un qui te poursuive et qui en veuille \u00e0 ta vie, l\u2019\u00e2me de mon seigneur sera li\u00e9e dans le faisceau des vivants aupr\u00e8s de l\u2019\u00c9ternel, ton Dieu, et il lancera du creux de la fronde l\u2019\u00e2me de tes ennemis.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Sam.25","name":"1 Samuel 25","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.25"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Sam.25.30","name":"1 Samuel 25:30","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.25.30"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Sam.25.28","name":"1 Samuel 25:28","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.25.28"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"30","lastverse":"30","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.25.30","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Sam.25.30","label":"","reference":"1 Samuel 25:30","prev_osis_id":"1Sam.025.029,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Sam.025.031,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Sam.25.30\" class=\"v\">30<\/sup>Lorsque l\u2019\u00c9ternel aura fait \u00e0 mon seigneur tout le bien qu\u2019il t\u2019a annonc\u00e9, et qu\u2019il t\u2019aura \u00e9tabli chef sur Isra\u00ebl,<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Sam.25","name":"1 Samuel 25","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.25"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Sam.25.31","name":"1 Samuel 25:31","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.25.31"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Sam.25.29","name":"1 Samuel 25:29","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.25.29"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"31","lastverse":"31","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.25.31","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Sam.25.31","label":"","reference":"1 Samuel 25:31","prev_osis_id":"1Sam.025.030,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Sam.025.032,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Sam.25.31\" class=\"v\">31<\/sup>mon seigneur n\u2019aura ni remords ni souffrance de c\u0153ur pour avoir r\u00e9pandu le sang inutilement et pour s\u2019\u00eatre veng\u00e9 lui-m\u00eame. Et lorsque l\u2019\u00c9ternel aura fait du bien \u00e0 mon seigneur, souviens-toi de ta servante.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Sam.25","name":"1 Samuel 25","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.25"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Sam.25.32","name":"1 Samuel 25:32","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.25.32"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Sam.25.30","name":"1 Samuel 25:30","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.25.30"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"32","lastverse":"32","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.25.32","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Sam.25.32","label":"","reference":"1 Samuel 25:32","prev_osis_id":"1Sam.025.031,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Sam.025.033,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Sam.25.32\" class=\"v\">32<\/sup>David dit \u00e0 Abiga\u00efl: B\u00e9ni soit l\u2019\u00c9ternel, le Dieu d\u2019Isra\u00ebl, qui t\u2019a envoy\u00e9e aujourd\u2019hui \u00e0 ma rencontre!<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Sam.25","name":"1 Samuel 25","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.25"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Sam.25.33","name":"1 Samuel 25:33","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.25.33"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Sam.25.31","name":"1 Samuel 25:31","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.25.31"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"33","lastverse":"33","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.25.33","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Sam.25.33","label":"","reference":"1 Samuel 25:33","prev_osis_id":"1Sam.025.032,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Sam.025.034,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Sam.25.33\" class=\"v\">33<\/sup>B\u00e9ni soit ton bon sens, et b\u00e9nie sois-tu, toi qui m\u2019as emp\u00each\u00e9 en ce jour de r\u00e9pandre le sang, et qui as retenu ma main!<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Sam.25","name":"1 Samuel 25","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.25"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Sam.25.34","name":"1 Samuel 25:34","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.25.34"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Sam.25.32","name":"1 Samuel 25:32","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.25.32"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"34","lastverse":"34","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.25.34","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Sam.25.34","label":"","reference":"1 Samuel 25:34","prev_osis_id":"1Sam.025.033,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Sam.025.035,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Sam.25.34\" class=\"v\">34<\/sup>Mais l\u2019\u00c9ternel, le Dieu d\u2019Isra\u00ebl, qui m\u2019a emp\u00each\u00e9 de te faire du mal, est vivant! Si tu ne t\u2019\u00e9tais h\u00e2t\u00e9e de venir au-devant de moi, il ne serait rest\u00e9 qui que ce soit \u00e0 Nabal, d\u2019ici \u00e0 la lumi\u00e8re du matin.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Sam.25","name":"1 Samuel 25","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.25"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Sam.25.35","name":"1 Samuel 25:35","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.25.35"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Sam.25.33","name":"1 Samuel 25:33","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.25.33"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"35","lastverse":"35","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.25.35","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Sam.25.35","label":"","reference":"1 Samuel 25:35","prev_osis_id":"1Sam.025.034,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Sam.025.036,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Sam.25.35\" class=\"v\">35<\/sup>Et David prit de la main d\u2019Abiga\u00efl ce qu\u2019elle lui avait apport\u00e9, et lui dit: Monte en paix dans ta maison; vois, j\u2019ai \u00e9cout\u00e9 ta voix, et je t\u2019ai favorablement accueillie.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Sam.25","name":"1 Samuel 25","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.25"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Sam.25.36","name":"1 Samuel 25:36","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.25.36"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Sam.25.34","name":"1 Samuel 25:34","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.25.34"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"36","lastverse":"36","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.25.36","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Sam.25.36","label":"","reference":"1 Samuel 25:36","prev_osis_id":"1Sam.025.035,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Sam.025.037,fra-LSG","text":"<h5 class=\"r\">V. 36-44: cf. 2 S 13:23, 24. (Ps 73. Pr 1:32; 10:21.) (Pr 18:22; 19:14.)<\/h5>\n<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Sam.25.36\" class=\"v\">36<\/sup>Abiga\u00efl arriva aupr\u00e8s de Nabal. Et voici, il faisait dans sa maison un festin comme un festin de roi; il avait le c\u0153ur joyeux, et il \u00e9tait compl\u00e8tement dans l\u2019ivresse. Elle ne lui dit aucune chose, petite ou grande, jusqu\u2019\u00e0 la lumi\u00e8re du matin.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Sam.25","name":"1 Samuel 25","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.25"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Sam.25.37","name":"1 Samuel 25:37","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.25.37"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Sam.25.35","name":"1 Samuel 25:35","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.25.35"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"37","lastverse":"37","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.25.37","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Sam.25.37","label":"","reference":"1 Samuel 25:37","prev_osis_id":"1Sam.025.036,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Sam.025.038,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Sam.25.37\" class=\"v\">37<\/sup>Mais le matin, l\u2019ivresse de Nabal s\u2019\u00e9tant dissip\u00e9e, sa femme lui raconta ce qui s\u2019\u00e9tait pass\u00e9. Le c\u0153ur de Nabal re\u00e7ut un coup mortel, et devint comme une pierre.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Sam.25","name":"1 Samuel 25","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.25"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Sam.25.38","name":"1 Samuel 25:38","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.25.38"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Sam.25.36","name":"1 Samuel 25:36","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.25.36"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"38","lastverse":"38","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.25.38","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Sam.25.38","label":"","reference":"1 Samuel 25:38","prev_osis_id":"1Sam.025.037,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Sam.025.039,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Sam.25.38\" class=\"v\">38<\/sup>Environ dix jours apr\u00e8s, l\u2019\u00c9ternel frappa Nabal, et il mourut.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Sam.25","name":"1 Samuel 25","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.25"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Sam.25.39","name":"1 Samuel 25:39","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.25.39"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Sam.25.37","name":"1 Samuel 25:37","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.25.37"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"39","lastverse":"39","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.25.39","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Sam.25.39","label":"","reference":"1 Samuel 25:39","prev_osis_id":"1Sam.025.038,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Sam.025.040,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Sam.25.39\" class=\"v\">39<\/sup>David apprit que Nabal \u00e9tait mort, et il dit: B\u00e9ni soit l\u2019\u00c9ternel, qui a d\u00e9fendu ma cause dans l\u2019outrage que m\u2019a fait Nabal, et qui a emp\u00each\u00e9 son serviteur de faire le mal! L\u2019\u00c9ternel a fait retomber la m\u00e9chancet\u00e9 de Nabal sur sa t\u00eate. David envoya proposer \u00e0 Abiga\u00efl de devenir sa femme.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Sam.25","name":"1 Samuel 25","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.25"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Sam.25.40","name":"1 Samuel 25:40","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.25.40"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Sam.25.38","name":"1 Samuel 25:38","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.25.38"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"40","lastverse":"40","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.25.40","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Sam.25.40","label":"","reference":"1 Samuel 25:40","prev_osis_id":"1Sam.025.039,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Sam.025.041,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Sam.25.40\" class=\"v\">40<\/sup>Les serviteurs de David arriv\u00e8rent chez Abiga\u00efl \u00e0 Carmel, et lui parl\u00e8rent ainsi: David nous a envoy\u00e9s vers toi, afin de te prendre pour sa femme.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Sam.25","name":"1 Samuel 25","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.25"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Sam.25.41","name":"1 Samuel 25:41","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.25.41"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Sam.25.39","name":"1 Samuel 25:39","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.25.39"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"41","lastverse":"41","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.25.41","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Sam.25.41","label":"","reference":"1 Samuel 25:41","prev_osis_id":"1Sam.025.040,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Sam.025.042,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Sam.25.41\" class=\"v\">41<\/sup>Elle se leva, se prosterna le visage contre terre, et dit: Voici, ta servante sera une esclave pour laver les pieds des serviteurs de mon seigneur.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Sam.25","name":"1 Samuel 25","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.25"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Sam.25.42","name":"1 Samuel 25:42","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.25.42"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Sam.25.40","name":"1 Samuel 25:40","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.25.40"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"42","lastverse":"42","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.25.42","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Sam.25.42","label":"","reference":"1 Samuel 25:42","prev_osis_id":"1Sam.025.041,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Sam.025.043,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Sam.25.42\" class=\"v\">42<\/sup>Et aussit\u00f4t Abiga\u00efl partit, mont\u00e9e sur un \u00e2ne, et accompagn\u00e9e de cinq jeunes filles; elle suivit les messagers de David, et elle devint sa femme.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Sam.25","name":"1 Samuel 25","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.25"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Sam.25.43","name":"1 Samuel 25:43","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.25.43"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Sam.25.41","name":"1 Samuel 25:41","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.25.41"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"43","lastverse":"43","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.25.43","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Sam.25.43","label":"","reference":"1 Samuel 25:43","prev_osis_id":"1Sam.025.042,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Sam.025.044,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Sam.25.43\" class=\"v\">43<\/sup>David avait aussi pris Achinoam de Jizreel, et toutes les deux furent ses femmes.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Sam.25","name":"1 Samuel 25","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.25"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Sam.25.44","name":"1 Samuel 25:44","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.25.44"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Sam.25.42","name":"1 Samuel 25:42","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.25.42"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"44","lastverse":"44","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.25.44","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Sam.25.44","label":"","reference":"1 Samuel 25:44","prev_osis_id":"1Sam.025.043,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Sam.026.001,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Sam.25.44\" class=\"v\">44<\/sup>Et Sa\u00fcl avait donn\u00e9 sa fille Mical, femme de David, \u00e0 Palthi de Gallim, fils de La\u00efsch.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Sam.25","name":"1 Samuel 25","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.25"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Sam.26.1","name":"1 Samuel 26:1","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.26.1"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Sam.25.43","name":"1 Samuel 25:43","id":"fra-LSG:1Sam.25.43"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"}],"meta":{"fums":"<script>\nvar _BAPI=_BAPI||{};\nif(typeof(_BAPI.t)==='undefined'){\ndocument.write('\\x3Cscript src=\"'+document.location.protocol+'\/\/d2ue49q0mum86x.cloudfront.net\/include\/fums.c.js\"\\x3E\\x3C\/script\\x3E');}\ndocument.write(\"\\x3Cscript\\x3E_BAPI.t('5af81fbab24814.83843203');\\x3C\/script\\x3E\");\n<\/script><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/d3a2okcloueqyx.cloudfront.net\/nf1?t=5af81fbab24814.83843203\" height=\"1\" width=\"1\" border=\"0\" alt=\"\" style=\"height: 0; width: 0;\" \/><\/noscript>","fums_tid":"5af81fbab24814.83843203","fums_js_include":"d2ue49q0mum86x.cloudfront.net\/include\/fums.c.js","fums_js":"var _BAPI=_BAPI||{};if(typeof(_BAPI.t)!='undefined'){ _BAPI.t('5af81fbab24814.83843203'); }","fums_noscript":"<img src=\"https:\/\/d3a2okcloueqyx.cloudfront.net\/nf1?t=5af81fbab24814.83843203\" height=\"1\" width=\"1\" border=\"0\" alt=\"\" style=\"height: 0; width: 0;\" \/>"}}}